  m_text: "Roles\n\nHunter - Tries to capture Runner  \n\nRunner -Tries to escape
    Hunter\n\n\nMatch Rules\n\nThe game is played in a Best-of-5 format.\n\nRoles
    swap every round.\n\nThe first player to win 3 rounds takes the match!\n\n\nControls\n\nW
    - Move Forward\n\nS - Move Backward\n\nA - Turn Left\n\nD - Turn Right"
